2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes an orientation-aware CNN framework for the icosahedron mesh, which involves machine learning techniques. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing a system for autonomous driving, which is an application of AI. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with omnidirectional images, which are often used in computer graphics. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing a system for autonomous driving, which is an application of robotics.
